nodes.text: FL-6198 was a First Order jet trooper who served in Omicron Formation. During the First Order's invasion of the planet Kashyyyk, FL-6198 was stationed alongside CR-1521 in the Black Forest. The Wookiee Chewbacca, part of a Resistance force sent to defend Kashyyyk, came across the two stormtroopers and knocked them both unconscious.
